strings: <voice_0x01001C69><se_high>media princess: I miss Prince Charming so much... I mean, he's a really nice guy, but I don't think so.
<voice_0x01001C6B><se_high>media princess: We must respect the novelty.
<voice_0x01001C6C><se_high>media princess: But... Do you think that will change after the wedding?
<voice_0x01001C70><se_high>media princess: Prince Charles' condition is improving...
